# Inference model weights are large (hundreds of MB) and live on the CDN.
# README, LICENSE, and meta.json next to each model ARE tracked so the layout,
# attribution, and SHA-256 are reviewable in-repo. The download script
# (scripts/download-inference-models.sh) populates the *.onnx files on demand.
/assets.opendaw.studio/models/**/*.onnx
/assets.opendaw.studio/models/**/*.onnx.partial
